

                                             Dear Customer, Welcome To  DKB BANK


We provide 3 types of loan
                                1. Personal Loan
                                2. Housing Loan
                                3. Gold Loan

Please refer below details for more information.

1. Personal Loan

Our customers are valuable for us. DKB Bank personal loan can be availed
by the customers with a good track record of one year or more.

* Interest rate 11.50 % p.a
* Maximum loan amount 30 Lakhs
* Low processing charge 0.1% only
* Simple documentation
* Fast processing
* Tenure Range from 12 to 72 Months

2. Housing Loan

DKB Bank helps you to build your dream home.

* Interest rate 8.90 % p.a
* Maximum loan amount 1 Crore
* Low processing charge
* Simple documentation
* Fast processing
* Tenure Range from 12 to 360 Months



3. Gold Loan

The scheme is intended to provide short term loans for people
who are urgently in need of money,on the security of gold ornaments.

* Maximum Amount per Gram
* Low interest rate
* Fast processing
* Maximum loan period 12 Months
* Maximum loan amount Rs 25 Lakhs per Individual, per day.

